Interface DatabaseOperationResult

All Superinterfaces:
OperationResult
All Known Implementing Classes:
CleanResult, DeleteResult, RepairmentResult, ValidationResult
public sealed interface DatabaseOperationResult extends OperationResult permits CleanResult, ValidationResult (not exhaustive)
A specialization of the OperationResult that always affects a database, either the default one or a named other.
Since:
1.2.0
Author:
Michael J. Simons
